text: Marzia Kjellberg ( Bisognin; born 21 October 1992) is an Italian Internet personality, fashion designer, and business person. She is known for her videos on her now-inactive YouTube channel. She has been married to Swedish YouTuber Felix Kjellberg. since 2019. ==Notes== ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Italian models Category:Italian fashion designers Category:YouTubers Category:Italian businesspeople
